author: Mr. Nobody
text: Every path is the right path. Everything could've been anything else.﻿ And it would have just as much meaning.

author: Mr. Nobody
text: Choices ... We cannot go back. That’s why it’s hard to choose. You have to make the right choice. As long as you don’t choose, everything remains possible.

author: Charles Dickens
text: if the world go wrong, it was, in some off-hand manner, never meant to go right.

author: Mr. Robot
text: A bug is never just a mistake. It represent something bigger, an error of thinking. That makes you who you are.

author: Elliot Alderson
text: We're all living in each other's paranoia
